{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 7''' is the 7th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Shōkyō|ja|正暦|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|June 19|ja|6月19日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The fall of the 【Rokuhara Tandai|六波羅探題】 in Kyoto occurred due to the attack by the forces of [[Ashikaga Takauji|足利尊氏]] who had turned against the bakufu. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1582]] {{ill|May 28|ja|5月28日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – During the campaign against the 【Mōri clan|毛利氏】, {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|12=draft|12=draft}} besieged the Ise province castle, {{ill|Takamatsu Castle (Binchū)|ja|備中高松城|12=draft|12=draft}}, using a naval blockade. * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 3|ja|6月3日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – During the summer siege of Osaka (【Ōsaka Natsu no Jin】), the Tenshu of Ōsaka Castle burned down. * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|12=draft|12=draft}} 16th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1703]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – At Takemotoza in Osaka, the puppet theater play (【Joruri】) “{{ill|Sonezaki Shinchū|ja|曽根崎心中|12=draft|12=draft}}” by {{ill|Chikamatsu Monzaemon|ja|近松門左衛門|12=draft|12=draft}} was first performed. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1872]] {{ill|June 12|ja|6月12日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The first railway in Japan began provisional service between Shinagawa Station and Yokohama Station (currently {{ill|Sakuragichō Station|ja|桜木町駅|12=draft|12=draft}}).
== Births == * [[Ōei]] 9th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1402]] {{ill|June 7|ja|6月7日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ichijō Kaneyoshi|ja|一条兼良|12=draft|12=draft}}, a waka poet (died [[1481]]). * [[Keichō]] 16th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1611]] {{ill|June 30|ja|6月30日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hoshina Masayoshi|ja|保科正之|12=draft|12=draft}}, the fourth son of {{ill|Tokugawa Hidetada|ja|徳川秀忠|12=draft|12=draft}} and lord of the Aizu Domain (died [[1673]]). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1730]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Motoori Norinaga|ja|本居宣長|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Kokugaku scholar (died [[1801]]). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1857]] {{ill|May 29|ja|5月29日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Itō Midaiharu|ja|伊東巳代治|12=draft|12=draft}}, a politician (died [[1934]]).
