qq-May 7 (Lunisolar)-qq {{Lunisolar May}} '''May 7''' is the 7th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安}}.
