* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1872]] {{ill|June 12|ja|6月12日|12=draft}}) – The first railway in Japan began provisional service between Shinagawa Station and Yokohama Station (currently {{ill|Sakuragichō Station|ja|桜木町駅|12=draft}}).

