== Events == * {{ill|Shōkyō|ja|正暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkyō|qq=}} 2nd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkō|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1333]] {{ill|June 19|ja|6月19日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 19|qq=}}) – The fall of the 【Rokuhara Tandai|六波羅探題】 in Kyoto occurred due to the attack by the forces of [[Ashikaga Takauji|足利尊氏]] who had turned against the bakufu. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1582]] {{ill|May 28|ja|5月28日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 28|qq=}}) – During the campaign against the 【Mōri clan|毛利氏】, {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=}} besieged the Ise province castle, {{ill|Takamatsu Castle (Binchū)|ja|備中高松城|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takamatsu Castle (Binchū)|qq=}}, using a naval blockade. * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genna|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 3|ja|6月3日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 3|qq=}}) – During the summer siege of Osaka (【Ōsaka Natsu no Jin】), the Tenshu of Ōsaka Castle burned down. * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genroku|qq=}} 16th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1703]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 20|qq=}}) – At Takemotoza in Osaka, the puppet theater play (【Joruri】) “{{ill|Sonezaki Shinchū|ja|曽根崎心中|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sonezaki Shinchū|qq=}}” by {{ill|Chikamatsu Monzaemon|ja|近松門左衛門|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chikamatsu Monzaemon|qq=}} was first performed. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1872]] {{ill|June 12|ja|6月12日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 12|qq=}}) – The first railway in Japan began provisional service between Shinagawa Station and Yokohama Station (currently {{ill|Sakuragichō Station|ja|桜木町駅|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakuragichō Station|qq=}}).
== Births == * [[Ōei]] 9th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1402]] {{ill|June 7|ja|6月7日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 7|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ichijō Kaneyoshi|ja|一条兼良|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ichijō Kaneyoshi|qq=}}, a waka poet (died [[1481]]). * [[Keichō]] 16th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1611]] {{ill|June 30|ja|6月30日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 30|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hoshina Masayoshi|ja|保科正之|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hoshina Masayoshi|qq=}}, the fourth son of {{ill|Tokugawa Hidetada|ja|徳川秀忠|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Hidetada|qq=}} and lord of the Aizu Domain (died [[1673]]). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1730]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 21|qq=}}) – {{ill|Motoori Norinaga|ja|本居宣長|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Motoori Norinaga|qq=}}, a Kokugaku scholar (died [[1801]]). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1857]] {{ill|May 29|ja|5月29日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 29|qq=}}) – {{ill|Itō Midaiharu|ja|伊東巳代治|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itō Midaiharu|qq=}}, a politician (died [[1934]]).
== Deaths == * [[260]] – {{ill|Cao Mao|ja|曹髦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Cao Mao|qq=}}, the 4th Emperor of Wei during the Three Kingdoms period (born [[241]]). * {{ill|Enkyū|ja|延久|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyū|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1073]] {{ill|June 15|ja|6月15日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 15|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Sanjō|ja|後三条天皇|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Go-Sanjō|qq=}}, the 71st Emperor of Japan (born [[1034]]). * {{ill|Ōei|ja|応永|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei|qq=}} 17th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1410]] {{ill|June 9|ja|6月9日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 9|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shiba Yoshimasa|ja|斯波義将|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiba Yoshimasa|qq=}}, a military commander and official of the Ashikaga Shogunate (born [[1350]]). * [[Genna]] 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1615, June 3) – {{ill|Sanada Yukimura|ja|真田信繁|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sanada Yukimura|qq=}} (also known as Yukimura, or "Kochi"), a military commander (born [[1567]]). * {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keian|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1650]] {{ill|June 5|ja|6月5日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Yosinobu|ja|徳川義直|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Yosinobu|qq=}}, the ninth son of Tokugawa Ieyasu and the first lord of the Owari Domain (born [[1600]]).
